{"tid":1162519,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港女嫁內地男 將佔跨境婚姻一半","createTime":"2019-05-20T02:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T02:43:50.000Z","uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"70796feec2955e87006c96ce23e8881ad96ed4da","tid":1162519,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:22:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%AB%81%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7-%E5%B0%87%E4%BD%94%E8%B7%A8%E5%A2%83%E5%A9%9A%E5%A7%BB-%E5%8D%8A-214500007.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AB%2581%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25BD%2594%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E5%25A2%2583%25E5%25A9%259A%25E5%25A7%25BB-%25E5%258D%258A-214500007.html&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ11MsCyrUT%2FuZDySwcdaP%2B5k%3D&h=5312df50\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%AB%81%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7-%E5%B0%87%E4%BD%94%E8%B7%A8%E5%A2%83%E5%A9%9A%E5%A7%BB-%E5%8D%8A-214500007.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3TAZ8WpRwYu1vxXZVFha4g--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-05/91c5d340-7a89-11e9-b92c-93718d4cb8c7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3TAZ8WpRwYu1vxXZVFha4g--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-05%2F91c5d340-7a89-11e9-b92c-93718d4cb8c7&h=630774b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港女嫁內地男 將佔跨境婚姻一半<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】跨境婚姻出現逆向北上新形勢，勞工及福利局局長羅致光昨表示，近年跨境婚姻已由八十年代「港男」北上娶妻，變成愈來愈多「港女」與內地男性結婚，這類婚姻在一七年已佔跨境婚姻總數達三成，預計未來十年港男港女涉跨境婚姻會大致相等。<br />\n<br />\n料赴港單程證需求漸減<br />\n<br />\n鑑於愈來愈多家庭選擇於內地團聚，且內地推出港人領取內地居住證等優化安排，預料未來單程證需求會逐步減少，可能令本港早於之前估計的二○四三年出現人口負縮長。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光昨日發表網誌，談到本港家庭狀況的變化及支援，他表示港人與內地居民的跨境婚姻一直存在，八十年代時，超過百分之九十五婚姻是「港男」北上娶妻，至○三年內地實施個人遊政策後，多了跨境婚姻在港註冊。<br />\n<br />\n羅表示，近年在港註冊的婚姻有三分之一屬於跨境婚姻，不論是團聚時的適應，或者是雙方選擇離婚的安排等，相關人士均會面對更大壓力，會增加對這類家庭的支援。<br />\n<br />\n另一類要加強支援的家庭是「混合式家庭」，即配偶雙方或配偶之一因再婚而重組的家庭，且子女之中最少有一人是與自己沒有血緣關係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊D港女肯嫁呀"},{"pid":"ecbc44443f744e1304cd9502bf87759426783ed8","tid":1162519,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:41:35.000Z","msg":"所謂港女，都係單程証嗰啲"},{"pid":"6f121ddd5e3fa0dc0b883fb0c4973674da962f8d","tid":1162519,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"新移民(7年後) =(香)港女(性)<br />\n<br />\n玩定義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}